{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.1", "text_original": "思樂泮水，薄采其芹。魯侯戾止，言觀其旂。\n其旂茷茷，鸞聲噦噦。無小無大，從公于邁。", "text_normalized": "思樂泮水，薄采其芹。魯侯戾止，言觀其旂。\n其旂茷茷，鸞聲噦噦。無小無大，從公于邁。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.2", "text_original": "思樂泮水，薄采其藻。魯侯戾止，其馬蹻蹻。\n其馬蹻蹻，其音昭昭。載色載笑，匪怒伊教。", "text_normalized": "思樂泮水，薄采其藻。魯侯戾止，其馬蹻蹻。\n其馬蹻蹻，其音昭昭。載色載笑，匪怒伊教。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.3", "text_original": "思樂泮水，薄采其茆。魯侯戾止，在泮飲酒。\n既飲旨酒，永錫難老。順彼長道，屈此羣醜。", "text_normalized": "思樂泮水，薄采其茆。魯侯戾止，在泮飲酒。\n既飲旨酒，永錫難老。順彼長道，屈此羣醜。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.4", "text_original": "穆穆魯侯，敬明其德。敬慎威儀，維民之則。\n允文允武，昭假烈祖。靡有不孝，自求伊祜。", "text_normalized": "穆穆魯侯，敬明其德。敬慎威儀，維民之則。\n允文允武，昭假烈祖。靡有不孝，自求伊祜。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.5", "text_original": "明明魯侯，克明其德。既作泮宮，淮夷攸服。\n矯矯虎臣，在泮獻馘。淑問如臯陶，在泮獻囚。", "text_normalized": "明明魯侯，克明其德。既作泮宮，淮夷攸服。\n矯矯虎臣，在泮獻馘。淑問如臯陶，在泮獻囚。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.6", "text_original": "濟濟多士，克廣德心。桓桓于征，狄彼東南。\n烝烝皇皇，不吳不揚。不告于訩，在泮獻功。", "text_normalized": "濟濟多士，克廣德心。桓桓于征，狄彼東南。\n烝烝皇皇，不吳不揚。不告于訩，在泮獻功。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 6."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__007__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.7", "text_original": "角弓其觩，束矢其搜。戎車孔博，徒御無斁。\n既克淮夷，孔淑不逆。式固爾猶，淮夷卒獲。", "text_normalized": "角弓其觩，束矢其搜。戎車孔博，徒御無斁。\n既克淮夷，孔淑不逆。式固爾猶，淮夷卒獲。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 7."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-003__008__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-003", "source_id": "song-lusong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·003.8", "text_original": "翩彼飛鴞，集于泮林。食我桑黮，懷我好音。\n憬彼淮夷，來獻其琛。元龜象齒，大賂南金。", "text_normalized": "翩彼飛鴞，集于泮林。食我桑黮，懷我好音。\n憬彼淮夷，來獻其琛。元龜象齒，大賂南金。", "notes": "泮水 Chinese stanza 8."}
